-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Feign
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- using interfaces to communicate with endpoints
- interfaces will be automatically implemented at runtime

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discovery aware Feign
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
- feign is a discovery-aware Spring RestTemplate
- instead of service-urls, it is using service-names
- no EurekaClient needed

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Discovery without Feign (with RestTemplate)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
we would have to autowire an instance of EurekaClient into our controller
with which we could receive a service-information by service-name as an
Application object

